<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.1.3">
<l>cēmamē vēṇṭit tīviṉai perukkit</l>
<l>terivaimā ruruvamē maruvi</l>
<l>ūmaṉār kaṇṭa kaṉavilum paḻutā</l>
<l>yoḻintaṉa kaḻintavan nāḷkaḷ</l>
<l>kāmaṉār tātai nammuṭai yaṭikaḷ</l>
<l>tammaṭain tārmaṉat tiruppār</l>
<l>nāmanā ṉuyya nāṉkaṇṭu koṇṭēṉ</l>
<l>nārā yaṇāveṉṉum nāmam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those days which have passed lusting for wealth,</l>
<l rend="indent">heaping up evil deeds, embracing the bodies of women,</l>
<l>Are wasted in ruin, [as] in dreams that mute people have seen.</l>
<l>[For] me to be saved, I discovered for myself the name</l>
<l rend="indent">of him who will be in the hearts of those</l>
<l>Who resort to him, our god, Kāma’s father,</l>
<l rend="indent">the name which is pronounced, “Nārāyaṇā!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
